    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“那么，我的职能和生命的意义是什么呢？”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:10.6085958Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:10.6085960Z",
      "original_text": "\"So, what is my function and the meaning of my life?\"",
