        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:10.6085976Z",
          "locale_text": "“那么，我的职能和生命的意义是什么呢？”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Alors, quelle est ma fonction ? Quel est le sens de ma vie ? »",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-15T08:02:29.7952761Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-15T08:02:29.7952762Z",
      "original_text": "\"So, what is my function and the meaning of my life?\"",
